    <div class="hero-label">Habitat Residency</div>
    <h1>Live and build<br><em>with other founders.</em></h1>
    <p class="hero-sub">You've already shipped an MVP. Now it's time to go deeper. Full immersion, dedicated mentorship, and a demo day in front of investors.</p>
    <div class="hero-meta">
      <div class="hero-meta-item">
        <span class="hero-meta-label">Format</span>
        <span class="hero-meta-value">Live-in</span>
      </div>
      <div class="hero-meta-item">
        <span class="hero-meta-label">Ends with</span>
        <span class="hero-meta-value">Demo day</span>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="hero-buttons">
      <a href="contact.html?program=residency" class="btn-primary">Join the waitlist &rarr;</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>



<!-- FOOTER -->
<footer>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="footer-grid">
      <div class="footer-brand">
        <div class="logo" style="font-size:20px">[Habitat]</div>
        <p>The fastest path from zero to real. Building across Belgium since 2025.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="footer-col">
        <h4>Programs</h4>
        <a href="https://luma.com/habitat" target="_blank">Evenings</a>
        <a href="hackathon.html">Technical Hackathons</a>
        <a href="residency.html">Residency</a>
      </div>
      <div class="footer-col">
        <h4>Community</h4>
        <a href="https://luma.com/habitat" target="_blank">Events</a>
        <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/company/joinhabitat">LinkedIn</a>
      </div>
      <div class="footer-col">
        <h4>Contact</h4>
        <a href="contact.html">Apply / Partner</a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="footer-bottom">
      <span>&copy; 2026 Habitat. Made with care in Belgium.</span>
      <span>Leuven &middot; Ghent &middot; Brussels &middot; Antwerp</span>
    </div>
